        "category": "Chicken",
        "area": "United States",
        "recipeDescription": "This is more of a loose soup than your mama's C&D, but it's super high protein, very low fat, and medium carb. And it's pretty darn tasty.",
        "dietType": 1,
        "prepTime": 30,
        "estimatedTime": 60,
        "allergens": [
            5,
            1
        ],
        "protein": 429,
        "fat": 62,
        "carb": 262,
